description: Header file defining a template interface for a generic iterator used within the WPEFramework RPC namespace. It declares an abstract interface class IIteratorType with methods for iteration control and querying.

classes.name: IIteratorType
classes.description: A template interface class for iterating over elements of type ELEMENT, identifiable by an interface ID. Provides methods for traversing, resetting, and retrieving elements.

methods.name: Next
methods.description: Advance the iterator to the next element, outputting it through the provided reference.

methods.name: Previous
methods.description: Move the iterator to the previous element, outputting it through the provided reference.

methods.name: Reset
methods.description: Reset the iterator position to the specified index.

methods.name: IsValid
methods.description: Check if the current iterator position is valid.

methods.name: Count
methods.description: Return the total number of elements in the collection.

methods.name: Current
methods.description: Return the current element pointed to by the iterator.
